trans-unit.source: Identifies an object as an add-in view segment of the pipeline.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer et objekt som et tillegg visningen segmentet pipeline.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInStore.Rebuild%2A> and <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInStore.Update%2A> methods, which maintain the store of information about available pipeline segments, use this attribute to identify an add-in view.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInStore.Rebuild%2A>og <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInStore.Update%2A>metoder, som har store opplysninger om tilgjengelig pipeline segmenter, Bruk attributten til 책 identifisere en visning som tillegget.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInStore.Update%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInStore.Rebuild%2A>

trans-unit.source: To construct the pipeline, the type in the add-in view that the add-in inherits from is identified by the AddInBaseAttribute attribute and is called the add-in base.
trans-unit.target: For 책 lage pipeline typen i tillegg visningen tillegget arver fra er identifisert av attributtet AddInBaseAttribute og kalles base tilleggsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: This attribute should be used only on types that activate the segments of the pipeline.
trans-unit.target: Dette attributtet kan bare brukes p책 typer som aktiverer segmentene for pipeline.

trans-unit.source: Types that represent objects passed between the host and the add-in do not need this attribute.
trans-unit.target: Typer som representerer objekter som sendes mellom verten og tillegget trenger ikke dette attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.AddIn.Pipeline.AddInBaseAttribute"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.AddIn.Pipeline.AddInBaseAttribute"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets one or more add-in base types that a single add-in-side adapter can use to construct the pipeline.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en eller flere tillegget basistyper ett enkelt legge til i side-kort kan bruke til 책 konstruere pipeline.

trans-unit.source: An array of add-in base types.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av tillegget enkle typer.
